Description: Terminal UI for monitoring and controlling systemd services
 lazysystemd is a terminal user interface (TUI) application for monitoring
 and controlling systemd services, inspired by lazydocker.
 .
 Features:
  - View service status with real-time updates
  - View and follow service logs
  - Start, stop, restart, and reload services
  - Simple keyboard-driven interface
